<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, height=device-height, initial-scale=1">

	<title>홈 화면</title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"> <!-- load bootstrap css -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.min.css"> <!-- load fontawesome -->

	<style>
		body { padding-top:80px; }

		@font-face {
			font-family: 'Nanum Gothic'; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;
			src: url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf');
			src: local('NanumGothic'),
			url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('embedded-opentype'),
			url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('woff2'),
			url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('woff'),
			url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('truetype');
		}

		h1, p, a { font-family: '배달의민족 주아' ; color : floralwhite}
	</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
	<div class="jumbotron text-center" style='background-image:url("/public/images/school1.jpg")'>
		<h1><div class="home" ></div> 선생님 로그인 화면</h1>
		<br>
        <% if (login_success) { %>
		<p>로그인되어 있습니다.</p>
		<br>
		<a href="/logout2" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>로그아웃</a>
        <% } else { %>
		<p>로그인하세요.<p>
		<p>계정이 없으시면 회원가입하세요.</p>
		<br>
		<a href="/login2" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>로그인</a>
		<a href="/signup2" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>회원가입</a>
		<br>

        <% } %>

	</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>